0018f-5d80-d0ec-a9cf-df9f751e0000</guid></item><item><title>土耳其在宣布贸易抵制一周后将发放有限的向以色列出口的许可证</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/turkey-to-grant-limited-permits-to-export-to-israel-a-week-after-announcing-trade-boycott/0000018f-5dd1-d995-a5df-5ff7f3e00000</link><description>土耳其商人冒着因抵制而遭受经济损失的风险，向埃尔多安施压，要求他重新考虑。但以色列制造商协会负责人认为放松限制只是“一种幻想”</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 16:02:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/turkey-to-grant-limited-permits-to-export-to-israel-a-week-after-announcing-trade-boycott/0000018f-5dd1-d995-a5df-5ff7f3e00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 216 天：据报道以色列谈判小组离开开罗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-216-israeli-negotiation-team-reportedly-leaves-cairo/0000018f-5e03-d9a0-a38f-fe2794fb0001</link><description>中央情报局局长在与内塔尼亚胡和摩萨德负责人会面后返回美国，并在开罗停留 ■ 哈马斯谈判代表团前往多哈，指责以色列试图进入拉法破坏停战谈判 ■ 世卫组织称只剩下三天的燃料加沙南部的医疗行动 ■ 超过 150 名以色列人拦截了前往加沙的约旦援助车队 ■ 战争开始 216 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 15:50:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-216-israeli-negotiation-team-reportedly-leaves-cairo/0000018f-5e03-d9a0-a38f-fe2794fb0001</guid></item><item><title>人工智能可以成为新闻业的生命线——或者是一根吊死自己的绳子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/tech-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/ai-could-be-a-lifeline-for-journalism-or-a-rope-to-hang-itself/0000018f-588f-d0ec-a9cf-de9ff6d70000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 15:24:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/tech-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/ai-could-be-a-lifeline-for-journalism-or-a-rope-to-hang-itself/0000018f-588f-d0ec-a9cf-de9ff6d70000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔在推特上发推文称哈马斯“喜欢”拜登，总统考虑因拉法问题停止美国向以色列运送武器</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-tweets-hamas-biden-as-president-mulls-halting-u-s-arms-shipments-to-israel/0000018f-5d25-d9a0-a38f-fd27f61e0000</link><description>以色列反对派领导人亚伊尔·拉皮德表示，本·格维尔的推文危及了“每一位以色列国防军士兵和每一位以色列公民”，而财政部长贝扎莱尔·斯莫特里奇则表示，“尽管有拜登的反对，我们仍将在这场战争中取得彻底胜利”</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 13:32:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-tweets-hamas-biden-as-president-mulls-halting-u-s-arms-shipments-to-israel/0000018f-5d25-d9a0-a38f-fd27f61e0000</guid></item><item><title>当以色列人发现我来自爱尔兰时，他们会问：“你为什么恨我们？”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-09/ty-article-opinion/.premium/when-israelis-find-out-im-from-ireland-they-ask-why-do-you-hate-us/0000018f-5cf6-d0ec-a9cf-deff36c10000</link><description>作为一名出生于爱尔兰、居住在特拉维夫的以色列记者，我被迫应对爱尔兰和以色列之间因加沙战争而不断恶化且经常公开敌对的关系。但我在都柏林的朋友和家人提出的一个问题我很难回答</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 13:23:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-09/ty-article-opinion/.premium/when-israelis-find-out-im-from-ireland-they-ask-why-do-you-hate-us/0000018f-5cf6-d0ec-a9cf-deff36c10000</guid></item><item><title>国家保险研究所数据显示，自 1851 年以来，已有 5000 多名以色列平民在恐怖袭击中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/over-5-000-israeli-civilians-murdered-in-terror-attacks-since-1851-national-data-shows/0000018f-5d47-d0ec-a9cf-df5f2ce60000</link><description>10月7日，以色列与哈马斯战争爆发，共有822名以色列平民被杀害，造成630名儿童成为孤儿，177人成为寡妇，693名父母失去亲人。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 13:19:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/over-5-000-israeli-civilians-murdered-in-terror-attacks-since-1851-national-data-shows/0000018f-5d47-d0ec-a9cf-df5f2ce60000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争期间以色列关系的场景</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-05-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/scenes-from-an-israeli-relationship-during-a-war-in-gaza/0000018f-572c-d209-a79f-572d4fdb0000</link><description>当罗特姆·科迪什的伴侣从加沙服役回来后，她发现自己无法像以前一样与他交谈，所以她开始画插图来描述他们所经历的事情。这个每日系列记录了他们最私密的问题，强调了夫妻在战争时期如何应对</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 12:19:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-05-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/scenes-from-an-israeli-relationship-during-a-war-in-gaza/0000018f-572c-d209-a79f-572d4fdb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列，孤立吗？不要相信你读到的一切</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/israel-isolated-dont-believe-everything-you-read/0000018f-5d32-d9a0-a38f-fd371d080000</link><description>土耳其与以色列断绝贸易关系是新闻，但其他 120 个国家没有断绝贸易关系并不是新闻。铁的事实仍有待浮出水面，但以色列不应自满</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 12:00:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/israel-isolated-dont-believe-everything-you-read/0000018f-5d32-d9a0-a38f-fd371d080000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡无视每一个警告。现在拜登告诉以色列：“够了”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-ignored-every-warning-now-biden-is-telling-israel-enough-is-enough/0000018f-5cc6-d0ec-a9cf-dedf3a680000</link><description>由于大约 3,500 枚炸弹的运输目前已停止，美国总统乔·拜登向总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡发出关于在加沙开展地面行动的明确信息</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 11:36:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-ignored-every-warning-now-biden-is-telling-israel-enough-is-enough/0000018f-5cc6-d0ec-a9cf-dedf3a680000</guid></item><item><title>数据显示，独立日前夕以色列人口达到 990 万</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/israels-population-reaches-9-9-million-on-eve-of-independence-day-data-reveals/0000018f-5cd7-d9a0-a38f-fcf7eb620000</link><description>据以色列中央统计局称，到明年独立日，以色列及其西岸定居点人口预计将超过1000万</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 10:51:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/israels-population-reaches-9-9-million-on-eve-of-independence-day-data-reveals/0000018f-5cd7-d9a0-a38f-fcf7eb620000</guid></item><item><title>以色列摩萨德首次承认：10月7日我们感到惊讶</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/israels-mossad-admits-for-the-first-time-we-were-surprised-on-october-7/0000018f-573f-d6a5-a5ff-d73f93e20000</link><description>尽管与其他组织相比，该情报机构对 10 月 7 日灾难性失败的责任微不足道，但它以多种方式参与了以色列在加沙的活动，主要是卡塔尔资金流向哈马斯</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 10:45:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/israels-mossad-admits-for-the-first-time-we-were-surprised-on-october-7/0000018f-573f-d6a5-a5ff-d73f93e20000</guid></item><item><title>蔑视、否认、忽视：以色列对哈马斯和 10 月 7 日事件的毁灭性情报失败的根源</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/disdain-denial-neglect-the-roots-of-israels-intelligence-failure-on-hamas-and-oct-7/0000018f-5811-d348-a7bf-feb907a80000</link><description>2021 年加沙战争结束后，以色列军事情报部门就加沙哈马斯的真正威胁做出了一系列重大决定。从压制不同意见到淘汰单位，“失败链”就是这样发生的</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 10:05:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/disdain-denial-neglect-the-roots-of-israels-intelligence-failure-on-hamas-and-oct-7/0000018f-5811-d348-a7bf-feb907a80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列顶级武器制造商无意中透露了其最大的外国客户：印度</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-defense-giant-iai-unwittingly-reveals-its-largest-foreign-customer/0000018f-583d-d348-a7bf-febdda230000</link><description>事实证明，去年印度占以色列航空航天工业公司出口收入的四分之一。以色列公司的年度报告中还披露了阿塞拜疆和摩洛哥的详细信息</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 09:14:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-defense-giant-iai-unwittingly-reveals-its-largest-foreign-customer/0000018f-583d-d348-a7bf-febdda230000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防雇员因严重性犯罪被监禁十多年</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-defense-employee-incarcerated-for-over-a-decade-for-severe-sexual-offenses/0000018f-5c54-d1d4-afcf-fc5e323c0000</link><description>十多年前，这位前国防机构雇员因滥用职权对其他雇员进行性伤害而被起诉，并被判犯有严重性犯罪罪</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 08:55:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-defense-employee-incarcerated-for-over-a-decade-for-severe-sexual-offenses/0000018f-5c54-d1d4-afcf-fc5e323c0000</guid></item></channel></rss>